pageTitle: Freejack Oak Park Pendant by Tech Lighting | 700FJOAKBAC
textBeforeTable: Craftsman-style four-sided glass shade with Black metal frame with White inner shade. Glass available in Amber, Havana Brown or Clear. Finish in Antique Bronze, Chrome or Satin Nickel. Includes one 50 watt 12V low voltage halogen bipin and six feet of field-cuttable cable suspension (custom lengths available). 7.3 inches long x 7.3 inches wide x 3.3 inches high.  ETL listed. textAfterTable: Dimensions: 7.3"L x 3.3"H x 7.3"W Lamp Source: Halogen Bulb: 1 x JC/GY6.35 (bipin)/50W/12V Halogen Bulb included Dimmer: Dimmable Download Specification Sheet  ETL About Tech Lighting Tech Lighting originally established its name as a leading designer of architectural lighting with its contemporary decorative fixtures and innovative low-voltage track lighting systems, including MonoRail, Kable Lite, TwinRail and, later, T-trak. The Tech brand has since evolved, with a portfolio offering an expansive selection of lighting solutions for both residential and commercial applications. Tech Lighting products span a wide variety of lighting categories, including low- and line-voltage decorative pendants, wall sconces, chandeliers, bath bars and bath lighting, picture lights, directional track heads and ceiling fixtures (both flush mount and suspension) all featuring timeless, original design. You'll find Tech Lighting in homes with the most beautiful and innovative kitchens, bathrooms, foyers, dining rooms, family rooms and bedrooms, as well as in well-appointed restaurants, hotels, boutiques, offices and retail stores domestically and abroad.
